AcceptDecideRule is a rule that accepts all urls. If you want to make
decisions based on some sort of business logic, you need to use other
rules. For instance you can use a DecideRuleSequence to chain together
rules, much like bean[@id=&#39;scope&#39;] does. Something like this:

&lt;property name=&quot;shouldFetchBodyRule&quot;&gt;
 &lt;bean class=&quot;org.archive.modules.deciderules.DecideRuleSequence&quot;&gt;
  &lt;property name=&quot;rules&quot;&gt;
   &lt;list&gt;
    &lt;!-- rule --&gt;
    &lt;!-- rule --&gt;
    &lt;!-- rule --&gt;
   &lt;/list&gt;
  &lt;/property&gt;
 &lt;/bean&gt;
&lt;/property&gt;

